    "An entry marked with \"•\" or non-blank signifies that the corresponding information is used as input, while a blank entry indicates its absence.",
    "The last column provides the reference for each study.From Table 14, we can see that numerous studies have emerged, employing a variety of deep learning techniques for defect prediction.",
